1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">  have talked=C2=A0about</a> the leveraged buyout of=C2=A0Citr=
ix Systems Inc., which was signed in January and closed last month. The mar=
ket was good in January and bad in September, so the banks who committed to=
 finance the Citrix deal <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/29427655.285505/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVz=
